"""
NDM (Net Deck Multiplier) Optimizer
=====================================
Simulates and optimizes deck configurations to maximise the Net Deck Multiplier.

Usage:
    python ndm_optimizer.py
    Deck configs are defined in the DECKS list near the bottom of the file.

Card-type key used in grid displays:
    R = Row    C = Col    S = Surr
    ^ = DirGreed(up)    v = DirGreed(down)
    < = DirGreed(left)  > = DirGreed(right)
    e = EvoGreed    o = SurrGreed    . = generic_greed
"""

